originalText.text: This company goes around the city movin cars and bike out of parking spots damaging everything they dont even have a permit to move car or bikes. They moved my motorcycle at 220 5av they ripped the whole cover talked to the one in charge on site he said he could do what ever he wants called the company they sais they will call me back they never called so i had to call back and then they told me to call next day to speak with the owner they havent answer since then. Becarefull with ur cars and bikes when u see a scaffold from these guys they think they own the street and will damage your stuff
